Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:06.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Skrugg's... spaceship! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so big... 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can believe anything now... 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kiddin' me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:02.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The chief told us to shoot that thing down with {\i1}these{i0}? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:05.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like takin' a grizzly down with your bare hands! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:09.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec... Please, tell me what's going on here... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:11.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really happening? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell should I know? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the report from the reconnaissance team? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:35.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Communications have remained silent. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter. Begin! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry Joey! Everyone evacuate! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:47.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, where should we run to? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:50.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were taught to gather at the city hall if something like this happened. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:51.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:04:59.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's in the direction of my house... 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:05.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to check on my grandma! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:06.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:17.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I've got this guy, I can handle it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:19.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get a move on. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:21.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me come, too! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You take care of the professor, Lina. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're countin' on you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:28.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:31.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:37.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you planning on going? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why the hell would we tell {\i1}you{\i0} something like... 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:41.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to my house. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:46.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not done talking here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:51.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to use that robot for? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:55.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan on becoming a hero or something? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:57.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really... 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:02.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never accept someone like {\i1}you{\i0} being a hero! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Will! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I'm doing is going home. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chickens like you should turn-tail and run! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:20.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:25.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! We've got to hurry and evacuate! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why those little... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't copy that... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please repeat. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to double check... This is not a joke, correct? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:06:59.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President, we have a matter of grave importance. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A matter of grave importance? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I take back what I said! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:30.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more like ants tryin' to stand up to an elephant! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:37.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we high-tail it out of here while we still can? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding... 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the army! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,America, hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How awful... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:49.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:50.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we let them pass by? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:55.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or bust 'em up with your pal there? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about my grandma. Let's wait for them to pass. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:08.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this, you cockroach sonofabitches! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:45.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, Joey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:50.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Balzac 1 to squadron... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Balzac 1 to squadron... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maintain formation. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Approach at low-altitude until 7 miles to target, then break, climb, and begin attack! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:07.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Copy that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go giving the ground any kisses now, you hear! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:19.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin attack! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evasive maneuvers! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reform and regroup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:57.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To think there would be such a difference in our powers. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:02.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is now nothing for us to fear. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:06.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed to the next step in the plan! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:18.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One at a time! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be fine. Calm down. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:33.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't broadcast that transmission, then this... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this wouldn't have... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:44.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:46.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:47.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen my brother? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was here a little while ago, but... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:53.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We came here together, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys hear where he was going? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, we don't know. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should ask Nick. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:02.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I haven't seen him around either. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:20.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you planning on doing, Will? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:26.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about sneaking into their saucer? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:27.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:32.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just see? Even the military is no match for them! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:33.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:34.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here. I have an idea. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:42.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to come, you know. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... I'll come, too! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:49.03,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stick with Will, I might get famous! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:53.03,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one that becomes the hero! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.30,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch, Psy, Joey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow the house looks like it's safe. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:15.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:24.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:37.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Your grandma comes first, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:38.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stop them! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:41.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they destroy any more, my grandma'll die of shock! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Heroman. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Joey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:47.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Time out! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Well... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:43.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Engage! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman, I'll fight, too! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:41.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't leave you alone. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:50.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:20.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:32.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Joey, Psy... Why are you here? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we here? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:36.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't notice? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Notice what? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:44.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, it's been quite noisy outside today. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:45.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something going on? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:50.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why aren't you two at school? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:19.30,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all living things on this planet. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:23.42,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all living things on this planet. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:28.14,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all living things on this planet. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.51,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Skrugg. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:32.43,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Rulers of the universe! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.46,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,To repeat: 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:37.19,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Skrugg. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:40.71,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Rulers of the universe! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:47.70,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,From henceforth we proclaim this planet as ours! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.53,0:21:57.28,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,This decision will not be overturned. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:22:00.96,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,We will eliminate all who resist without mercy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:04.15,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,To repeat: 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:06.27,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Skrugg. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:09.24,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Rulers of the universe! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:24.09,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"Can you hear this voice?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:31.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been calling that, always, from deep within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:45.46,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you, all alone, let another lonely one be next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:51.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because together it's not lonely, it's twoly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:56.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you're not alone any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:22:59.99,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because there's no one next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:02.54,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't mean that I'm lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:07.74,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone to notice this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:13.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,that heart must have surely cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:16.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we'll crush to bits
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.65,0:23:20.35,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the fortress of our limitless sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:24.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:27.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? I'm running through at full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:31.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,To where you're waiting, left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:34.64,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,in the place of tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:39.77,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you, with burning passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:43.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:52.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Heroman: 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:53.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? 
